{"type":"message","id":"4c780b67","parentId":"c7c0436a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:18:48.187Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-23 20:18 EDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Build a React web app for Bobby's AI Agent Mission Control dashboard. \n\nDesign: iOS 26 liquid glass / frosted glass aesthetic — translucent panels, backdrop-blur, soft glows, dark background (#08080e), clean Apple-like UI. Frosted glass cards with `backdrop-blur(20px)`, subtle white borders, indigo/violet glow accents.\n\nTech stack: React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS.\n\n**CRITICAL - Gateway API lessons (must follow exactly):**\n\nThe OpenClaw gateway runs at `http://localhost:18789`. It requires Authorization Bearer token `286caba2a7d072f065abdec6f5cff840c2c31eb8f7801111`.\n\nTo call gateway tools from the browser, use Vite proxy in vite.config.ts:\n```ts\nserver: {\n  proxy: {\n    '/tools': {\n      target: 'http://localhost:18789',\n      changeOrigin: true,\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\nAnd set `VITE_GATEWAY_URL=http://localhost:5173` (the app's own origin, going through proxy).\n\n**Gateway session data structure (IMPORTANT):**\n- POST `/tools/invoke` with `{\"tool\":\"sessions_list\",\"args\":{}}`\n- Response: `{ok: true, result: {content: [{type:\"text\", text: \"...\"}], details: {count: N, sessions: [...]}}}`\n- The sessions are in `result.details.sessions` — a flat array of session objects\n- Each session has: `key` (string like \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\"), `updatedAt` (unix ms), `status` (\"done\"|\"running\"|\"active\"), `endedAt` (unix ms or null)\n\n**Agent ID mapping:**\n- Bobby's agents use these IDs in session keys:\n  - dean → \"main\" (his session keys start with `agent:main:`)\n  - emmy → \"emmy\"\n  - x → \"x\"  \n  - finn → \"finn\"\n  - yoyos → \"yoyos\"\n  - rex → \"rex\"\n  - dj → \"dj\"\n  - cody → \"cody\"\n  - martha → \"martha\"\n\n**Status determination:**\n- online: session updated in last 30 seconds\n- busy: session has status \"running\" or \"active\" and no endedAt\n- offline: no recent sessions or no sessions at all\n- error: only if session status is \"failed\"\n\n**Features to build (Phase 1):**\n1. Header with \"Mission Control\" title, live clock (HH:mm:ss), gateway connection indicator (green dot when connected, yellow when polling, red when disconnected)\n2. Agent grid — 9 agent cards in a responsive grid (3 cols desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile)\n3. Each agent card: emoji avatar (🤖🦋⚡🧊🎥🔍🎧💻🌿), agent name, role subtitle, status badge (online=green glow, busy=purple pulse, offline=gray, error=red), last active time\n4. Click agent → open frosted glass modal with textarea to send message (just a toast \"Message sent via Telegram!\")\n5. Loading skeleton cards while data loads\n6. Auto-poll every 3 seconds\n\n**Message sending:** Use the gateway tool invoke:\n- POST `/tools/invoke` with `{\"tool\":\"message\",\"args\":{\"action\":\"send\",\"channel\":\"telegram\",\"target\":\"8212808444\",\"message\":\"...\"}}`\n\n**Wire up the app properly:**\n- `src/lib/gateway.ts` — functions: `listSessions()` (fetches and parses from result.details.sessions), `sendMessage(message)` (invokes message tool)\n- `src/hooks/useAgentStatus.ts` — polls sessions_list every 3s, derives status per agent using the agent ID→session prefix mapping, returns `{agentStates, connectionState}`\n- `src/App.tsx` — composes everything\n- Use Tailwind for all styling — frosted glass via `backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl`\n\n**IMPORTANT:** Build it right the first time. Test the gateway API call structure before building the UI. Make sure the data flows correctly: gateway → parse → state → UI.\n\nOutput the project to `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/`\n\nAfter building, run `npm run build` to create a production `dist/` folder.\n\nWrite SPEC.md first, then build. Make it look INCREDIBLE — this is a premium iOS 26 visionOS-style dashboard."}],"timestamp":1774311528186}}
