{"type":"message","id":"c9054ecd","parentId":"cd29570e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:23:26.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything looks good. Let me also quickly verify the vite.config.ts is correct with the proxy and that the .env file is there.\n\nLet me also quickly verify the key files look correct. The build succeeded and everything is in place.\n\nLet me provide a summary to the main agent.","thinkingSignature":"689f946e4ce961b14b00a9e17ab5540f82301c9aed8b34b62a0bc53e5b093a1b"},{"type":"text","text":"The Mission Control dashboard is fully built and compiled. Here's a summary:\n\n**What was built:**\n- React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS project at `/Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/`\n- `SPEC.md` written first, then all source files built to spec\n- Production `dist/` folder generated successfully (202KB JS, 16KB CSS gzipped)\n\n**Project structure:**\n```\nsrc/\n  lib/gateway.ts          — listSessions() + sendMessage() via Vite proxy\n  hooks/useAgentStatus.ts — polls every 3s, derives agent status\n  types/index.ts          — Agent, AgentState, Session, AGENTS array\n  components/\n    Header.tsx            — live clock + connection indicator\n    AgentCard.tsx         — frosted glass card with emoji, badge, timestamp\n    AgentGrid.tsx         — responsive 3/2/1 col grid\n    StatusBadge.tsx      — online/busy/offline/error with glow effects\n    MessageModal.tsx     — textarea + send, keyboard shortcuts\n    SkeletonCard.tsx     — shimmer loading placeholder\n    Toast.tsx            — bottom-center auto-dismiss notification\n  App.tsx                 — composes everything\n  index.css               — global styles, animations, fonts\n```\n\n**Key design decisions:**\n- iOS 26 visionOS liquid glass aesthetic — `backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10`\n- Deep void background `#08080e` with subtle indigo radial gradient overlay\n- Status pulse animation on busy agents (violet glow breathing)\n- Shimmer skeleton loading before first API response\n- Gateway proxy: `/tools` → `http://localhost:18789` (no auth token needed in browser)\n- Agent prefix mapping: Dean→`agent:main:`, others as specified\n\n**To run:**\n```bash\ncd /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control\nnpm run dev    # dev server at http://localhost:5173\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19896,"output":477,"cacheRead":16563,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36936,"cost":{"input":0.0059688,"output":0.0005723999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009937799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007534979999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774311796941,"responseId":"06110c7431cae305e4c882ae895adc18"}}
